&lt;li&gt;Stay current with industry trends and advanced AI/ML, including agentic frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a key resource and contributor, lending your expertise to adjacent projects, special initiatives, and strategic conversations that align with your core competencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with delivery, engineering, and sales to define scope, identify opportunities, and evolve the Gemini Enterprise offering.

